<p class="govuk-body">Because the pandemic meant you missed out on having a normal induction, we can offer 2 things to help:</p>

<ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
  <li>a 5% timetable reduction to use on induction training this academic year. Your school should organise this</li>
